From ab05e50ec44506dc81220a21fb8f5e8d048772e0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Keith Winstein <keithw@cs.stanford.edu>
Date: Wed, 6 Sep 2023 15:54:12 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Share reading/validation code between elem exprs & other
 const exprs (#2288)

This continues the work from #1783 and reduces special handling of elem
exprs, by treating them the same as other const expressions (init
expressions).
